snippet.title: Workers & Resources: Soviet Republic - Biomes DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Build a Soviet superpower across three new biomes: the scorching desert, the unforgiving tundra, and the lush tropics, each with its own challenges and opportunities with the Biomes DLC for Workers & Resources: Soviet Republic! This DLC releases on June 20th, 2024 alongside the 1.0 release of the base game. 

Establish a glorious nation from the ground up on unpopulated maps, or explore populated maps that feature existing small towns with architecture fitting their respective biomes, begging to be united by a visionary leader.

➤ STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/24...
➤ GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/workers_r...
➤ EPIC: https://store.epicgames.com/p/workers...
